  <div class="bw-help-center__panel is-active" id="help-panel-my-order" role="tabpanel" data-help-panel="my-order">
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-header">
      <span class="bw-help-center__panel-eyebrow">My Order</span>
      <h3 class="bw-help-center__panel-title">Order placement, payment, and confirmation</h3>
      <p class="bw-help-center__panel-copy">Use this section for the most common order questions, from browsing to payment confirmation and post-purchase changes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary">
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Best for</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Checkout and confirmation</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Fast route</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Contact support</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">If it is project-led</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Open estimate desk</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__faq">
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item is-open">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          <span>How do I place my order?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Browse the range, open a product, choose the size, color, and variant, add it to cart, and continue browsing or check out from the cart icon.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How do I check the product size?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Dimensions sit under the product description, and the site also uses an image size scale to help with fit.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How will my order arrive?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Orders are packed with three-layer protection and shipped through partner courier companies.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How will I know my order is confirmed?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">You will receive email and SMS updates after purchase. The order is confirmed after payment verification is complete.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can I add an item after I place my order?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">No. Once the order is placed, items cannot be added to it.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bw-help-center__panel" id="help-panel-shipping-delivery" role="tabpanel" data-help-panel="shipping-delivery">
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-header">
      <span class="bw-help-center__panel-eyebrow">Shipping &amp; Delivery</span>
      <h3 class="bw-help-center__panel-title">Delivery timing, shipping modes, and tracking</h3>
      <p class="bw-help-center__panel-copy">This section groups the logistics questions shoppers ask most before and after dispatch.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary">
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Best for</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Delivery timing</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Fast route</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Track an order</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">If delayed</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Contact support</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__faq">
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How does Bluewud ship orders?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Products go through a three-step quality check before shipping, and Bluewud uses partner courier companies to deliver orders.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>When is my Order Shipped?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Orders are generally shipped within a day or two. If there are delays, relevant information is shared.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>When is the order delivered?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">The live page notes an estimated 10-12 working days from shipment, though delivery often happens sooner.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What's the difference in Air shipping &amp; Surface Shipping?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Items under 1.5 kg ship by air with an estimated 2-4 working day delivery. Heavier volumetric items ship by surface with an estimated 10-12 working day delivery.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How Do I Track My Order?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">A tracking ID is shared once the order is dispatched from the warehouse.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can I expect delivery on all days of the week?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Deliveries are expected on all seven days except national and state holidays.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bw-help-center__panel" id="help-panel-cancellations-related" role="tabpanel" data-help-panel="cancellations-related">
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-header">
      <span class="bw-help-center__panel-eyebrow">Cancellations &amp; Related Queries</span>
      <h3 class="bw-help-center__panel-title">Order edits, cancellation rules, and refunds</h3>
      <p class="bw-help-center__panel-copy">A focused area for shoppers who need to change or stop an order after purchase.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary">
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Best for</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Edits and cancellations</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">Fast route</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Email support</span></div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-card"><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-label">If already shipped</span><span class="bw-help-center__panel-summary-value">Follow support flow</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="bw-help-center__faq">
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How do I cancel my order?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">COD orders can be canceled from the registered account before shipping. For prepaid orders, contact care@bluewud.com to request a refund cancellation.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>If the order is shipped already, can I still cancel it?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Once shipped, the order cannot be canceled. If possible, refuse the shipment. If you already accepted it, you can return it and exchange it.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can I request changes or edits in my order?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Yes. Bluewud asks customers to email the support team with change requests so the team can help wherever possible.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bw-help-center__faq-item">
        <button class="bw-help-center__faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What happens if a payment was deducted but the order failed?</span><span class="bw-help-center__faq-icon">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="bw-help-center__faq-answer">Check your bank or card account first. If the account was debited, banks usually roll it back within about 10 business days. You can also write to care@bluewud.com for assistance.</div>
      </div>
